  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "ゲームボーイ用の多くの未翻訳の日本のゲームの一つです。これはRPGで、アレサトリロジーの三作目にあたります。あなたは女の子を操作し（アレサやアレサIIのキャラクターよりも年上で可愛らしい）、都市や森、野原などをさまよいながら、無数の敵とターンごとに戦います。",
      "lang": "ja",
      "source": "romu"
    },
    {
      "text": "Aretha III is a top-down fantasy RPG and the third game in the Aretha trilogy, developed by Japan Art Media and published by Yanoman. It was only released in Japan.",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "igdb"
    },
    {
      "text": "Materia, who blocked Howard's ambitions twice, lived a peaceful life again. Doole, who returned to the Kingdom of Aretha after her training journey, was surprised to find that Aretha's ring had been lost, but Materia did not seem to care at all. Ben Marxist, an old friend of mine, appeared in front of them and offered a story. He said, \"Are you willing to go to the Kingdom of Aretha 20 years ago?\" Materia, who thinks of her parents who were born and never seen, travels with Doole to the past kingdom of Aretha.",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "igdb_storyline"
    }
  ],
